  "text": "A CG model of the E. coli inner membrane was constructed, using the previously published lipidomic analysis [CITATION_1] . While the composition of the inner membrane of E. coli has many different types of lipids, the CG approximation, using the MARTINI force field [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] , results in only 9 different types of lipids, shown in supplementary table S2. The CL model was taken from [CITATION_4] , with the addition of a second species containing 2 unsaturations instead of 4.",
